---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Areas from "../../components/Areas.astro";
import CTA from "../../components/CTA.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="Locking Wheel Nut Removal | Tyre Emergency Ltd"
    description="Expert locking wheel nut removal services in Nottingham & Newark. Safe, quick, and efficient removal for any vehicle make and model."
>
    <section
        id="hero"
        class="text-center text-white d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center"
    >
        <div class="container">
            <p class="fw-bold display-5">
                Struggling with a Locking Wheel Nut?
            </p>
            <p class="lead fs-3">
                Safe and Efficient Removal for Any Vehicle Make and Model
            </p>
            <a
                href="tel:01636330055"
                class="btn btn-lg btn-warning fw-bold text-secondary"
                ><i class="bi bi-telephone-fill"></i> Get Help Now</a
            >
        </div>
    </section>
    <main>
        <div class="text-center py-5 bg-light">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="fw-bold text-center">
                    Professional Locking Wheel Nut Removal Services
                </h1>
                <h2 class="mb-5 text-warning fw-bold">Mobile Service Available Across Nottingham & Newark</h2>
                <p class="lead">
                    Locking wheel nuts are essential for keeping your wheels
                    secure, but when you lose the key or encounter a stubborn
                    nut, they can become a significant headache. That's where
                    Tyre Emergency comes in. We offer professional locking wheel
                    nut removal services to drivers throughout Nottingham and
                    Newark.
                </p>
                <p class="lead">
                    Our team is equipped with specialized tools and expertise to
                    safely remove locking wheel nuts from any make and model of
                    vehicle, without damaging your wheels or tyres. Whether
                    you're at home, work, or stranded roadside, we're ready to
                    provide quick and reliable assistance.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container py-5">
            <h2 class="fw-bold text-center">
                Why Choose Tyre Emergency for Your Wheel Nut Removal?
            </h2>
            <ul class="lead">
                <li>
                    <strong>Expert Technicians:</strong> Our technicians are
                    highly trained and experienced in the removal of all types
                    of locking wheel nuts.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Fast and Convenient:</strong> Our mobile service
                    means we come to you, making the process as convenient as
                    possible. We aim to get you back on the road quickly with
                    minimal disruption to your day.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Service for All Vehicles:</strong> No matter what
                    type of vehicle you have, we have the tools and skills to
                    handle its locking wheel nuts effectively.
                </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="lead">
                If you're facing a locking wheel nut challenge, don't hesitate
                to call Tyre Emergency. Our friendly team is ready to provide
                you with efficient, hassle-free service, wherever you are in
                Nottingham or Newark.
            </p>
        </div>
    </main>
    <CTA/>
    <Areas />
    <CTA/>
</Layout>
<style>
    #hero {
        min-height: 60vh;
        background: linear-gradient(
                0deg,
                rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.9),
                rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.9)
            ),
            url("/img/locking-wheel-nut-removal.jpeg");
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
    }
</style>
